# 👋 Hi there! I'm Tobias Cerutti Gothe

🎓 Systems Engineering student at **UTN FRC**  
💻 DevOps Intern at **PSI - UNC**  
🚀 Passionate about backend development and infrastructure automation  
🌎 Currently learning English to improve my communication skills

---

## 🧑‍💻 About Me

- 🎓 I'm currently studying Systems Engineering at UTN FRC.
- 💼 I work as a DevOps intern at PSI (UNC), where I manage servers and automate tasks using **Bash**, **Docker**, **Ansible**, **Grafana**, and **Telegraf**.
- 🌐 I have basic knowledge of **HTML**, **CSS**, **JavaScript**, and **React** for frontend development.
- 🐘 I interact with **PostgreSQL** databases and understand **SQL**.
- ☕ I'm interested in **backend development** using **Java** and **Spring Boot**, and I'm building personal projects with this stack.
- 📦 I built a fullstack university project using **React** (frontend) and **Node.js** (backend).
- 🔧 I use **Git** daily for version control in my projects.
- 🌍 I'm actively learning English to reach professional fluency.

